::DEEPBLUE::
DEEPBLUE walks up the to predacon base.
"PREPARE TO DIE HE SCREAMS!"
He charges head first at full speed and rams the base with all of his might. 
  He gets up, a bit rattled but still determined.
"THIS BATTLE IS MINE!"
DEEPBLUE then opens his mouth reaal wide and starts starts gnawing on the 
hull.
"IM GONNA EAT YOU ALL ALIVE!"
DEEPBLUE slowly unholsters his double plasma relay.
"So you wanna play hardball eh?"
He grasps it tightly in his hands, charges once more, and starts bashing the 
hull with the butt of the gun.
"ANYONE ELSE THINK THEY CAN TAKE ME?"
